# loggings
Provides more logging tools.

## Installation
```sh
$ pip install loggings
```

## Usage
```py
>>> import loggings

>>> loggings.warning("hello")
WARNING:root:hello

>>> loggings.get_logger("here", loggings.DEBUG).debug("hello")
DEBUG:here:hello
```

